# Mobile UI standards

- **Viewport:** design for narrow phones first (`max-w-lg`, full-width cards).
- **Touch targets:** minimum **48px** height on buttons; **56px** for primary actions.
- **Typography:** `text-base` (16px) minimum on inputs to prevent iOS zoom.
- **Theme:** dark slate (`bg-slate-950`, cards `bg-slate-900/80`, borders `border-slate-800`).
- **Accent:** emerald for success/primary; amber critical; sky informational.
- **Layout:** one primary action per card; stats/labels above fold; no horizontal scroll.
- **Accessibility:** semantic buttons, `aria-label` on icon-only controls, sufficient contrast.
